    "body": "Hi @LeiWang1999 @zhangnju, this PR extends the AMD RDNA WMMA path to better support `gfx11` while keeping `gfx12` behavior intact. This implementation is based on PR #1951 and fixes Issue #1984 . Here are the main changes:\r\n\r\n- add RDNA-generation-aware WMMA codegen for HIP so `gfx11` and `gfx12` emit the correct builtin ABI\r\n- refactor WMMA layout selection to use per-architecture factories in the emitter\r\n- add `gfx11`-specific fragment modeling for duplicated half-wave ownership via replicated `T.Fragment`\r\n\r\n## Detailed Changes\r\n\r\n- `src/target/codegen_hip.cc`\r\n  - select the correct WMMA builtin form for `gfx11` vs `gfx12`\r\n  - update operand vector typing for RDNA WMMA codegen\r\n- `src/target/codegen_hip.h`, `src/target/rt_mod_hip.cc`, `src/target/utils.h`, `src/target/utils.cc`\r\n  - plumb `Target` into HIP codegen and add RDNA generation helpers\r\n- `tilelang/intrinsics/wmma_layout.py`\r\n  - split layout definitions by architecture\r\n  - add layout factory helpers\r\n  - add `gfx11` fragment-forward helpers for duplicated half-wave ownership\r\n  - add `A_colmajor` support for `gfx11&gfx12`\r\n- `tilelang/intrinsics/wmma_macro_generator.py`\r\n  - cache architecture-selected layout functions in `WMMAIntrinEmitter`\r\n  - use architecture-specific formulas for `local_size_a/local_size_b`\r\n  - model `gfx11` A/B fragment ownership with `forward_fn + replicate=2`\r\n  - add A_colmajor shape infer support for gfx11&gfx12\r\n\r\n## Why\r\n\r\n`gfx11` WMMA differs from `gfx12` in two important ways:\r\n\r\n- input operands use a different ABI/layout shape\r\n- logical A/B fragment elements are duplicated across the two half-waves\r\n\r\n## Validation\r\n\r\n- Using this PR, I successfully run the amd flash attention fwd/bwd example on gfx11 (including AI Max+ 395 (RX8060S iGPU) and PRO W7900 (**which is provided py @zhangnju**)) and gfx12 (RX9070XT) GPUs:\r\n\r\n* RX8060S FWD:\r\n<img width=\"1639\" height=\"244\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/1292bee0-64c4-4bd2-9394-475596f78bce\" />\r\n\r\n* RX8060S BWD:\r\n<img width=\"1159\" height=\"313\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/8cc97204-ec24-428f-bb4c-7c215e42835a\" />\r\n\r\n* W7900 FWD:\r\n<img width=\"2190\" height=\"241\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/d7ad04a2-f1ea-446a-af13-b814fcd29bf1\" />\r\n\r\n* W7900 BWD:\r\n<img width=\"895\" height=\"240\" alt=\"image\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/3f650a02-4246-4a1d-8d86-62fbad659dd2\" />\r\n\r\n* RX 9070XT FWD:\r\n<img width=\"501\" height=\"105\" alt=\"6563e3cc-e0cb-4766-b336-dc0ac501d513\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/7c9160fe-0849-4ae9-9dc7-46422b78e622\" />\r\n\r\n* RX 9070XT BWD:\r\n<img width=\"575\" height=\"163\" alt=\"596b677b-d693-47c8-8920-7ed8ecc9ecc6\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/0c4b42b5-e0c8-4257-8658-3a42a3aaa607\" />\r\n\r\n- @petersktang also successfully ran the above tests on **Radeon 890m (see the comments for more details)**.\r\n\r\n<!-- This is an auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->\n## Summary by CodeRabbit\n\n* **New Features**\n  * RDNA generation detection (gfx11/gfx12) propagated to HIP codegen, emitters, and examples; example helper to select RDNA-specific kernels/configs.\n\n* **Improvements**\n  * WMMA builtins, operand packing, fragment replication, and shared-memory load/store layouts parameterized per RDNA generation for improved correctness and performance.\n  * Kernel search spaces and data-flow adjusted for RDNA constraints.\n\n* **Bug Fixes**\n  * Unsupported RDNA generations now produce explicit errors.\n<!-- end of auto-generated comment: release notes by coderabbit.ai -->",
